Additional Close Code for InfoSec Assignment group on Incident Form. Used the UI Policy and created below script of addOption & removeOption

Execute if True condition :
function onCondition() {
g_form.addOption('close_code','User Compromised','User Compromised');
g_form.addOption('close_code','Device Compromised','Device Compromised');
g_form.addOption('close_code','Correction Applied','Correction Applied');
g_form.addOption('close_code','Awareness Raised','Awareness Raised');
g_form.addOption('close_code','Legitimate Activity','Legitimate Activity');
}


Execute if False condition :
function onCondition() {
g_form.removeOption('close_code','User Compromised');
g_form.removeOption('close_code','Device Compromised');
g_form.removeOption('close_code','Correction Applied');
g_form.removeOption('close_code','Awareness Raised');
g_form.removeOption('close_code','Legitimate Activity');
}
